products.name: Dog Charm
products.description: The Dog Charm is a delightful piece that captures the essence of man's best friend. This charm is perfect for animal lovers, featuring a playful dog design that adds a touch of whimsy to any outfit. Whether you're layering it with other charms or wearing it solo, this piece is sure to start conversations and show off your love for pets.

products.name: Gold Core Bangle
products.description: The Gold Core Bangle is a sleek and modern addition to any jewelry collection. Crafted with a simple yet elegant design, this bangle is perfect for those who appreciate minimalist style. The gold finish adds a touch of luxury, making it suitable for both casual and formal occasions.

products.name: Green Aventurine Moon Ring
products.description: The Green Aventurine Moon Ring is a stunning piece that combines the beauty of natural stone with celestial design. The green aventurine stone is believed to bring luck and opportunity, while the moon shape adds a mystical touch. This ring is perfect for those who love unique and meaningful jewelry.

products.name: La Perla Hoops
products.description: The La Perla Hoops are a classic choice for any ear. These elegant hoops are designed to be both timeless and versatile, making them a staple in any jewelry box. The perfect size for everyday wear, they add just the right amount of shine to any look.

products.name: LABRADORITE MOON RING
products.description: The LABRADORITE MOON RING features a captivating labradorite stone set in a moon-shaped ring. Labradorite is known for its iridescent quality, reflecting a spectrum of colors that can mesmerize the eye. This ring is a beautiful statement piece for those who appreciate the magic of natural gemstones.

products.name: LARGE SUGAR EARRINGS

These earrings feature a unique sugar-like texture that catches the light, creating a sparkling effect. Perfect for special occasions or for those who love to stand out, these earrings are sure to turn heads.
